OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells in the
OL,7,Fevening. Staying dry in the east
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells. Turning
OL,9,Fcloudier in the west overnight, with
OL,10,Fthe odd light shower.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry with bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells through much of the day,
OL,14,Fsomewhat cloudier in the west. Some
OL,15,Frain spreads east in the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
